House sits on 3 lots and has 2 addtnl lots available.  This home has many amenities ie, sky lights, many ceiling fans, continuous hot h2o heater, full house generator, large pantry room, propane & elec heat, water filter, whole house fan, storm doors, & decorator glass front door.
